metadata.name: Beginning Of The New Me
metadata.description:
Beginning Of The New Me

This Piece Describes a situation in my life that can't be described in words.

Started the year by Beginning my journey in Web3 Art Community After a year of putting in the craft and thinking about it, I've always wanted to make an original piece as an artist, and this artwork is the first of many original pieces.
This Artwork is a Combination of Traditional and Digital art Methods Created in Photoshop.
Always Grateful for the cool people and Goat Artists I met through my art, and it's just the start.
